1. *Gladni* smo jer nismo doručkovali. (We are *hungry* because we didn't have breakfast.)
2. Imamo *gladnih* u svijetu više nego ikad prije. (There are more *hungry* people in the world than ever before.)
3. *Gladan* sam pice. (I am *hungry* for pizza.)
4. Ako se *gladni* nahvataju za gušu, samo jedu. (When *hungry* people get hold of something to eat, they just eat.)
5. Nikada nisam videla *gladnu* bebu. (I have never seen a *hungry* baby.)
6. Sutra će biti hladno i *gladno* vreme. (Tomorrow will be cold and *hungry* weather.)
7. Oni su uvijek *gladni* novih avantura. (They are always *hungry* for new adventures.)
8. *Gladni* ljudi često traže hranu u smeću. ( *Hungry* people often look for food in the garbage.)
9. *Gladnom* čovjeku ni slanina ne smrdi. (To a *hungry* man, even bacon doesn't stink.)
10. Nema ničeg boljeg od toplog obroka kada si *gladan*. (There is nothing better than a warm meal when you are *hungry*.)